Maude Hirst https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Maude_Hirst 0 Maude Hirst (February 6, 1993) is a British actress mostly known for her role as Helga on The History Channel TV show Vikings between 2013 and 2017. Hirst studied drama arts at the renowned London school Italia Conti Academy of Theatre Arts.
